{
  "text": "These assays were performed as previously described [CITATION_1] . Briefly, 10 ml aliquots of normal human serum (NHS) were collected from three different donors. Half of these aliquots were heated by incubation for 30 min at 56\u00b0C to inactivate complement factors.",
